This is a very abbreviated credit list.  We couldn't possibly enumerate all
the people who have been involved in XPilot, especially since we have no such
list at hand. :)  If you find someone (yourself!?) missing from this list
then please don't hesitate to complain to the authors at xpilot@xpilot.org.

xpilot.org is:

    Bert Gijsbers           xpilot@xpilot.org
    Dick Balaska
    Kimiko Koopman
    Mark Boyns              DNS services
    Scott Adkins            www, ftp, and meta2 services
    Dick Balaska            mail services
    uni-Tromso, Norway      meta services

